So, we tried to think of some things that non-business user types would do with a 128GB iPad.  
Here is what we came up with. . . 
 
The maximum file size of an iOS app is 2GB, so you can fit 64 size-capped apps

A scene release of an episode of Family Guy is usually around 60MB to 90MB, with an average of 75MB. So, you can fit 1,747 Family Guy episodes (sorry, there are only 199 episodes total). George R. R. Martin's A Game of Thrones on iBooks is 11.3MB, so you could read 11,599 digital copies of the book, assuming you remove the one you just finished before starting on the next identical copy

CALL NOW  
  
 
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: iPad 3G Wi-Fi + 4G-AT and T-64GB
description:
iPad 3G-Wi-Fi + 4G-AT and T-Black-64GB-OS V-10, including the following accessories:   
	Apple iPad Smart Cover -- Dark Gray (new and unused) 
        Logitech Ultrathin Bluetooth keyboard/cover magnetic clip for iPad

        Stylus

The iPad and each accessory for it have been well cared for, seen little use, are in excellent working condition, with no scratches and include boxes and documentation.  The iPad has been updated to the most current OS version 10, and has had all data reset, so it is ready for a new owner.  It can be used with Wi-Fi or AT and T.  The iPad is 9.5" x 7.31" x 0.34" and weighs 1.35 pounds. 
 
The iPad Smart cover protects the screen without covering the back.  An aluminum hinge magnetically aligns the cover with the iPad and can be set up to wake on open and to sleep on close.  It can be folded back to tilt the iPad to type using the iPads internal keypad.  It can also be folded to make a movie or use as a Facetime stand. 
 
The Logitech keyboard/cover and stand is ultra-thin, Bluetooth wireless, and includes USB to micro USB charging cable.  It is very well designed, weighs less than 12 ounces and attaches using the same hinging mechanism as Apple's Smart Cover (magnetically).  When attached and closed it protects the screen and puts the iPad to sleep.  When removed, an angled slot behind the keyboard holds the iPad at a comfortable angle for typing. 
 
The Logitech UE Mobile Boombox/Speaker is a wireless Bluetooth speaker for the iPad, tablet, or phone and that doubles as a speakerphone for hands-free calls; it is ultra portable with 10-hour rechargeable battery. 
 
The Motorokr S305 Bluetooth wireless Headset allows you to manage your music using On-ear-music-controls to play, pause, next, previous, and volume - all from the headset.  It is rechargeable, and includes all documentation.   
 
The 30-pin digital AV adapter (there is an extra one) plugs into the iPad; the other end has two plugs: one for a HDMI cable (not included) which plugs into a screen or TV, and the other to plug into a USB cable to charge your iPad.  This can be used to watch HDMI movies on a larger screen without running out of power. 
 
The Apple iPad 10W USB Power Adapters (there is an extra one) are designed to plug into an electrical power outlet and into the iPad to charge it, or to plug into a USB port on your computer to sync it with iTunes or charge it.  Its USB plug plugs into its electrical plug.   
 
The Steampunk embroidered fabric carry case and Steampunk Gelaskin cover and wallpaper are included if desired; the Gelaskin covers the front and back of the iPad, is thin and tough scratch resistant and easily removed if not desired.  The fabric embroidered carry case is rigid yet soft enough to provide excellent protection for the iPad. 
 
The stylus can be used in place of fingers if desired.

HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT?
  
 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
SAVE $$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$ CALL NOW 
  
 
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
CALL AND SAVE TIME AND MONEY 
  
 
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: travel around while u work
description:
WHO WE ARE:  
• We are a global, exclusive, invitation-only travel club  
• We are a 10 year old company on track to do a billion dollars in revenue this year. 
• We are in all 50 United States and 26+ countries. 
• We have a world class training system and opportunities for mentor-ship 
• We have won several World Travel Awards and many other awards 
• We have our own foundation and partner with many well-known foundations to build schools, provide clean drinking water and to change lives in our own communities as well as around the world. 
 
WHO WE ARE LOOKING FOR: 
This is a unique opportunity that many feel like is a dream come true. With that said, it is not for just anyone. We are looking for a unique few that enjoy vacationing often, helping others, are forward-thinking, loves social media/making new friends and are looking for a way out or around the rat-race.  
If this sounds like you we want to encourage you to apply. **Not a corporate job position** 
 
 
RIGHT CANDIDATE MUST. . .: 
 
• Have integrity  
• Be a pleasure to work with 
• Be an out of the box thinker 
• Have interpersonal /social skills 
• Be familiar with social media sites 
• Smart phone 
• Laptop/iPad 
• Reliable transportation  
 
OPPORTUNITY DESCRIPTION: 
• Home-based opportunity  
• Vacation 4+ times a year  
• Part-time to start with the option of becoming full time. 
 
WHAT WE DO: 
We go on amazing vacations that our company creates and plans for us, we then take great pictures and share them with our friends/family/everyone using social media avenues such as Facebook, Instagram, Snap Chat. . .etc. (things we do already only with us you get paid for doing it). 
Break down: 
Amazing vacations + take great pictures + post to social media = work 
 
You will be working closely with our team either in person or remotely via Skype/ZOOM or phone to promote our travel club. Will train the right candidate(s).  
 
COMPENSATION: 
Substantial earning potential. Paid in several different ways. To be discussed further during interview process. 
 
CONTACT: 
Please submit a short summary of your skills and why you would be a good fit for our team to the email address provided by craigslist. PLEASE INCLUDE YOUR CITY IN THE SUBJECT LINE. 
 
*****This is an exciting, unique opportunity for those who want to travel the world, make a difference helping others and earn a living by living instead of the "normal" alternative. If that is you then we are looking forward to hearing from you!*****

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
JUST MAKE A CALL 
  
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
  
 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
ONE CALL 
  
 
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

2000 Fisher Tracker Freedom 200 DLX Pontoon boat.

Fully Double Bimini tops that zipper together to form 1 large top that shades the entire boat.  A must have in Arizona so you don't get burned. 
 
New radio, with MP3 and Aux-in for all of your music from iPhone, iPad or other music device. 
 
Hummingbird Fish finder with water temp and depth finder.  Built in cooler / live fish storage behind the captains chair.  no need to have another cooler taking up space. 
 
Trailer has ladder/stairs on front for easy loading and unloading, and pontoon boat trailer guide bunks for easy loading and unloading.  You just drive it up and it lines itself on the trailer.  Really cool and easy.   
 
Most of the pictures were taken on 10/27/17 at Canyon Lake.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

The VSX-42 is ready to bring you entertainment from new sources such as smartphones, tablets, PCs, select Android™ devices and thumb drives. It's the next step in a tradition of firsts, starting as a leader in embracing the Apple® lifestyle. Specifically designed to be compatible with iPod®, iPhone®, and iPad® devices, your receiver comes with a front panel USB port and USB/video cable to access all your music, videos, streaming content, and photos without buying a separate dock. And new for 2012, the USB port has been upgraded to handle uncompressed 192KHz/24-bit FLAC and WAV music files for true audiophile-level performance. 
 
Plus, since your iPhone, iPod and iPad charge automatically when connected, it's the ultimate plug-and-play integration with your home theater. Enjoy music with iTunes® album art, share videos and movies, downloaded TV shows from iTunes, photos, web content from YouTube® and much more. Got a call? Your iPhone mutes when you receive it. When it comes to control, use the Apple device directly or push a single button on the VSX-42's front panel to switch control to the included preset remote and intuitive on-screen menu. 
 
VSX-42 delivers stellar home theater performance, bringing the latest technological advances in an elegant package. With 560 watts of clear audio reproduction, the VSX-42 gives you connectivity options for your latest high-definition home theater components, and digital 1080p video from any source.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: Lifespan tr3000e electronic folding treadmill
description:
New in box 
 
The TR3000e Electric Folding Treadmill combines advanced fitness technology with the convenience of eFold storage.  
 
The 20" wide x 56" long running surface features 8 independent impact-absorbing bumpers, making it comfortable to run for extended durations.  
 
The 2.75 HP drive motor and premium running deck combine with the automatic step counter, 3-speed cooling fan, USB port, and dynamic exercise program to create a unique exercise experience.  
 
The console includes 17 preset workouts: 5 weight loss, 5 healthy living and 7 sports training.  
 
The speed range of 0.5 - 12 MPH and 15 incline levels offer a large array of workout options.  
 
The eFold technology folds the treadmill electronically with the press of a button, folding to 39" long x 33" wide x 66" high.  
 
While folded, the treadmill can easily be rolled for storage. Unfolded, the treadmill measures 70.25" long x 33" wide x 55" high.  
 
Bluetooth compatibility (LifeSpan Bluetooth adapter purchased separately) allows you to track your workouts and connects you with free LifeSpan Active Trac and Train & Trac apps that work with your Android device or iPad. Please note that only the LifeSpan Bluetooth adapter is compatible with the treadmill.  
 
The residential warranty covers a lifetime on the frame and motor, 5 year parts and 1 year of labor

title: 1985 Winnebago Chieftan 22
description:
I bought this two years ago for my winter solo boondocking around Arizona and Nevada.  Used it a few times, maybe 1000 miles and then my wife, who liked staying home up north, had a stroke, and all our lives changed for good.  After much shopping I settled on this one because the investment, licensing and insurance costs are all low for an classic unit and the second owner I bought it from had done all the upgrades and maintenance. Fuel costs for a gas unit had dropped in half. It was and is in great shape with near new tires and brakes, new Bilstein shocks, new steering gear, front air bags and a recent transmission rebuild with new transmission cooler. 
 
Two awnings are in good shape.  It has custom storage compartments on the back and top.  AC blows cold and it is set up for Mr. Heater propane connection inside so the furnace fan does not need to run while boondocking and use house batteries. 
 
Three way fridge, built in propane with a high pressure tap for things that run straight off cylinders, two outside showers with sinks that attach outside, one under the main awning for outside cooking/food prep.  See one with spice rack sitting in the shower. 
 
There is a bed in the back, a drop down bed over the captain's chairs and the dinette drops down for a bed. 
 
Stereo is nice with big woofer and set up for ipad.  CB radio.  Custom 70 gallon aux fuel tank in addition to the factory 40 (for extended range and buying gas where the price is good.)  Also nice for fueling toys. Powered by GM 454 that starts and runs fine. The first owner had installed new or rebuilt heads and the compression checked out even and within spec when I bought it. 
 
Unit is stored at Camp Verde near Cottonwood where is was always based since new and was not subject to emissions testing there or as presently licensed in Oregon.   Not working are the original engine ac and emission controls.  I hauled a 3500 lb trailer from Camp Verde to Roosevelt and back over hwy 260.  Original manuals included.
attributes: 1985 Winnebago Chieftain 22 good 8 cylinders rwd gas 108000 22ft clean automatic

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
call now 
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: Photographic Card Deck of The Elements: With Big Beautiful Photographs
description:
About the Author 
Theodore Gray is the author of The Elements: A Visual Exploration of Every Known Atom in the Universe; Theo Gray's Mad Science: Experiments You Can Do At Home, But Probably Shouldn't; Mad Science 2: Experiments You Can Do At Home, But Still Probably Shouldn't; and Popular Science magazine's "Gray Matter" column. With his company Touch Press, Gray is the developer of best-selling iPad and iPhone apps, including The Elements, Solar System, Disney Animated, The Orchestra, The Waste Land, and Skulls by Simon Winchester. He lives in Urbana, Illinois. 
Product Description 
A companion to the bestselling book The Elements: A Visual Exploration of Every Known Atom in the Universe , this beautiful photographic card deck features all 118 elements in the periodic table. One element per card appears as a full-size image on the front and fascinating information about the element on the back.  
 
The Photographic Card Deck of The Elements is the most detailed, lush, and beautiful set of cards ever produced on the subject of the periodic table.  With 126, 5"X5" cards in all, it includes one card for every one of the 118 elements, plus additional cards that explain the arrangement of the periodic table, present the elements sorted by various properties, and suggest activities and uses for the cards.  
   
The front side of each card shows a full-size, photographic image of the element, while the back gives scientific information including atomic weight, density, melting and boiling point, valence, and the percent of the element found in the universe, in the Earth's crust, in oceans, and in humans.  Graphics show melting/boiling points, density, electron configuration, and atomic radius.  A fascinating fact about the element, as well as the date of its discovery, is also included.  
 
The cards are perfect for students but also make an excellent gift for a scientist or anyone who enjoys the beauty and diversity of the natural world.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

(see below for all details). Here is some info pulled of off the web on the VSX-30:  
 
Elite receivers have always represented the utmost commitment to the artist's original vision. Combining audio and video processing technologies found nowhere else in their class with multiple professional-level control options, all Elite receivers possess the capability to elevate your entertainment experience beyond what you've ever expected. And with an eye towards total home theater integration thanks to connectivity with analog, digital, and network sources in addition to maximum audio and video precision, these receivers are your solution for a completely unrivaled home entertainment control center. 
 
The "Made for iPhone" certified VSX-30 effortlessly incorporates your Apple products into your home theater. And with Pioneer's exclusive iControlAV app (downloaded separately via the Apple App Store) your iPhone, iPad, or iPod touch is transformed into a full-function remote control. Hardly an entry-level Elite receiver, the VSX-30 supports a host of connectivity options for all your latest high-definition home theater components, plus audio support for two zones. RS-232 support means compatibility with the latest professional home automation systems from control leaders like Crestron and Control. And the VSX-30 brings extensive connectivity for your digital media via Ethernet and a front A/V input, and compatibility with Bluetooth sources (using the optional AS-BT100 adapter, sold separately). 
 
The Ultimate iPhone Experience--Now In Your Home Theater 
 
"Made for iPhone" Certification Provides iPhone Users the Ultimate Integration for their Home Theater 
Get a truly plug-and-play iPhone experience in your home theater. Thanks to the VSX-30's "Made for iPhone/iPod/iPad" certification, you can enjoy music with iTunes album art, movies, downloaded TV shows from iTunes, photos, web and more. An included USB/composite video cable makes connecting your iPhone to share your favorite media easy--and your iPhone charges automatically when connected. This included cable also works with most generations of iPod Classic, Nano, and iPod Touch. 
 
Share your videos, and enjoy music with full album information and album art on your TV. Your iPhone device's wireless and network features remain fully functional and music and movies will mute when you receive an incoming call. And you've got lots of control options--use the iPhone directly, or push a single button on the VSX-30's front panel to switch control to the included preset remote and an intuitive, full-color GUI. 
 
Pioneer's Free iPhone App Turns Your iPhone, iPad, or iPod touch into a Powerful Control Center 
Pioneer's iControlAV (a free download from Apple's App Store) gives you total control over your home theater sound. With controls for master and per-zone volume, sound fields, and more, you've got a simple but powerful way to adjust your home theater sound any way you like. 
 
The iPhone, iPad, and iPod touch device's accelerometer are used to control the balance, bass and dialogue--no confusing sequence of remote buttons to remember, just tilt and maneuver your Apple portable device until the sound is right where you want it. 
 
Where Maximum Fidelity Meets Connectivity 
 
Access Your Portable Devices, Internet Radio, and More 
In addition to connections for all your home theater components, a front USB port lets you connect your digital camera or portable media player to display a slideshow of JPEG photos on your HDTV, or play MP3, WAV, or WMA music files with full ID3 tag and album art support. Elite receivers will display up to 32 album art thumbnails on your TV, and you can scroll through them with the included remote. And your options don't stop with your portable devices. When connected to your home network, the VSX-30 is your portal for thousands of Internet radio stations -- all just a few clicks of the remote away. 
 
Full-Color On-Screen GUI 
There are more ways to control your Pioneer VSX-30 than just your iPhone. There's a full-color on-screen GUI for use with the included learning remote, so you can make guided adjustments to your home theater sound. Not only that, but all Elite receivers let you connect a USB keyboard so you can rename stations for radio and Internet radio, network settings, and more. 
 
Release Your Smartphone's Music with the AS-BT100 Bluetooth Adapter (sold separately) 
For wireless connectivity, add a Pioneer AS-BT100 Bluetooth adapter (sold separately) to release your music from your iPhone, iPad, Blackberry, or Android smartphone as well as other Bluetooth-enabled sources like laptops. It's a plug-and-play solution for listening to your smartphone's digital music library. And Pioneer's exclusive Sound Retriever AIR restores critical audio data that is often removed from compressed audio formats, especially when transferred via Bluetooth. 
 
 
How Pioneer's Technology Delivers the Ultimate Home Theater Experience 
 
The Latest HDMI Technology Gets You Ready for 3-D 
All of Pioneer's latest receivers support the latest HDMI 1.4a specification, meaning that you're not just getting the most out of your existing movies and music, you're preparing for the next generation of 3-D video content with the VSX-30. And with 4 HDMI inputs, you've got more than enough connectivity options for the growing number of high-definition sources available today. 
 
1080p Upscaling from Any Source 
Pioneer has long been the leader in video processing and the VSX-30 is no exception. Anchor Bay (VRS) Video Reference Series video processing lets you upscale your picture to digital 1080p from virtually any source, including analog. Additionally, 3D Noise Reduction and a suite of video adjustments ensure you'll get the best picture possible from anything you've got. 
 
True-to-Life, High-Definition Audio and New Dolby Pro Logic IIz 
Of course all the latest Pioneer receivers support high-definition audio formats like Dolby TrueHD and DTS-HD Master Audio to give your Blu-ray Disc movies a soundtrack that's true-to-life. But Pioneer adds an extra dimension with support for Dolby Pro Logic IIz across its entire 2010 line of receivers, which adds a "height" channel for an exciting new surround sound option. 
 
Near Studio-quality Sound with Advanced MCACC 
Pioneer's exclusive Multi-Channel Acoustic Calibration system (MCACC) provides a near studio-quality, multi-channel listening experience that customizes each of the VSX-30's 7.1 sound channels specifically to your listening environment. 
Additionally, the Auto Level Control feature can equalize volume level differences between tracks playing from a portable audio device or commercials during television programming so the volume can be enjoyed at a consistent level--no more jarring "blare" when switching audio sources. 
 
Where the VSX-30 truly shines is with custom control options. Full custom feature-sets including 2-zone Audio as well as partnerships with 3rd party controllers like Control4, Crestron and AMX ensure compatibility with the latest home automation technologies. 
 
All of these technologies come together in the VSX-30 to deliver an unprecedented level of control and sophistication for the serious home entertainment enthusiast.

HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
call and save 
  
 
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.
